{
  "stem": "10252.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quite unusual those days for Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he tried to make it survive by taking in partners that were not Jewish, but one day, they just came in, and they said, take your coat and leave.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how it was taken away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was before the Nazis came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that probably would be in about '41, '42.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was whispers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no announcements or nobody that we knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even the Jews had-- were afraid to talk among themselves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So one day, this one-- we-- we heard that might have been taken to labor camp and, next, somebody else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my father was taken away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He, actually, was taken away from Nyiregyhaza, but my mother got this doctor's letter and went to see him and got him released to come back home.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was, again, sometimes, we wondered, in retrospect, that he would have been better off-- had he been in a labor camp, he might have survived.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- he-- he-- we thought we saved him by bringing him back home because he really was a very sick man-- a young man and a very sick man-- stomach, always had stomach problems.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was, finally, at the end-- that's how he died in concentration camp because of the bad stomach.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother had connections with a doctor, took a letter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I guess, some financial arrangements were made, and my father was allowed to come back home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Exactly.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The yellow star was the beginning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the least of the problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "About two, three weeks later, they showed a certain part of the town which became the, so-called, ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our home became part of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were right in the center of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
